First update the apt package repository cache of your Debian operating :
	sudo apt-get update
	sudo apt-get install openssh-server
	run the command to start OpenSSH server :
	sudo systemctl start ssh

	find the IP address of the computer running the SSH serve
	ip a
in mode ssh :
	connect to this machine from another computer :
	ssh USER@HOST/IP

in mode graphique :
open 
like FileZilla, and  go to > file > site Manager > New Site
and rempli the information
